      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-mind-map-show-the-design-process-from-my-point-of-view&#34;&gt;The mind map show the design process from my point of view&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;https://FlomeWorld.github.io/img/software-design.png&#34; alt=&#34;image info&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
